{"tid":2147838,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明星幕後】10件事重新認識「國民妹妹」IU！負債家庭長大捐8億給家扶，這就是李知恩的溫暖與堅韌","createTime":"2020-08-09T13:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T10:05:08.000Z","uid":34643,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d5618b95634fa01849d1ed1081a3f150bab3ce41","tid":2147838,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/iu-%E6%9D%8E%E7%9F%A5%E6%81%A9-1592068502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fiu-%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2581%25A9-1592068502.jpg&h=d8b77d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關於「國民妹妹」IU李知恩你了解多少呢？外界認為的人生勝利組IU其實在負債家庭中長大，受盡親戚的冷言冷語，還住在充滿蟑螂的房間，不過這些經歷都是她努力的動力，出道僅2年就替家裡還清債務，還不間斷的捐款給兒童機構，ELLE整理了8件生活小事讓大家了解IU的溫暖與堅韌⋯<br />\n<br />\n1. 在負債家庭長大<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6sRIlFAXlU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6sRIlFAXlU&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=231554c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6sRIlFAXlU&h=24a77c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6sRIlFAXlU</a><br />\n大家對IU的印象可能都是16歲就走紅的「國民妹妹」， 但其實她不是所謂的人生勝利組，IU在負債累累的家庭中長大、受盡親戚的嘲諷，住在充滿蟑螂的小房間裡⋯她曾說過：「好險我在音樂裡找到歸屬，不然如果走偏的話一切就完了！」<br />\n<br />\n2. 曾經因為試鏡被詐騙<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BeaaQarHFxQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBeaaQarHFxQ&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=8b7d38e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBeaaQarHFxQ&h=b3bb8240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BeaaQarHFxQ</a><br />\n為了成為一名藝人，IU積極的尋求試鏡機會，但涉世未深的她卻被詐騙集團以培訓練習生的名義騙走一大筆錢，不過真正令人心碎的不是多少錢，而是那些錢是IU奶奶讓她追尋夢想的積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n3. 走紅後立馬幫爸爸買夢想車<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/0wt0RVgG3G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2F0wt0RVgG3G&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=2d78064f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2F0wt0RVgG3G&h=99519e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/0wt0RVgG3G</a><br />\n大家對IU最初的印象應該就是《Good Day》的三段高音吧～直到IU真正走紅，賺到了足夠的錢後，她不像一般的女孩買東西犒賞自己，而是立馬幫家裡還清債務，還幫爸爸買了夢寐以求的車子！<br />\n<br />\n4. 只有高中學歷<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bcz3aiZHt8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBcz3aiZHt8p&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=8e8822ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBcz3aiZHt8p&h=be711ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bcz3aiZHt8p</a><br />\n看起來氣質非凡的IU其實只有高中學歷，之前上節目被問到為什麼不考慮完成學業？她就笑笑的說：「我不怎麼喜歡唸書，在高中的時候我就已經確定自己不會唸大學了，而且以我當時的成績我應該什麼學校都進不了！」只要有自己想追求的事，也不用為了符合社會眼光去違背自己的意願，這就是IU的直率！<br />\n<br />\n5. 蟬聯3年韓國最喜愛的偶像<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CAur6icjZVe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAur6icjZVe&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=411ae871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAur6icjZVe&h=7005ae7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CAur6icjZVe</a><br />\nIU從出道以來人氣就像當高，之前在韓國蓋洛普民調中就蟬聯3年「韓國最喜愛的偶像」，其實這都是因爲IU對待粉絲就像家人一樣，她曾說過：「I代表我，U代表粉絲，希望兩者能一直相連」，這麼暖的名字怎麼能不愛！<br />\n<br />\n6. 非常喜歡閱讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BZJXjb9nN1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBZJXjb9nN1I&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=8bc362a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBZJXjb9nN1I&h=f42fe007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BZJXjb9nN1I</a><br />\n雖然IU沒有選擇上大學，不過從她的歌曲創作、文筆就可以感覺到IU的對於文字相當敏銳，而這一切都是因為她對閱讀的熱愛！IU曾分享：「我爸媽從來沒打罵我，每當我做錯事他們就會給我一本厚厚的書要求我看完，一點一滴的成就了我對閱讀的習慣。」<br />\n<br />\n7. 曾患有暴食症<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1yo4RHAUQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1yo4RHAUQE&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=c28eaa65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1yo4RHAUQE&h=15e5ab6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1yo4RHAUQE</a><br />\n你絕對沒想過身材如此纖細的IU竟然曾患有神經性暴食症，這是一種進食障礙，通常都是因為壓力等精神狀況所引起。IU曾表示：「我那段時間壓力真的太大，一點點事情就可能會擊垮我，因為心情太萎靡，除了睡覺以外的時間我都在暴飲暴食。」<br />\n<br />\n8.友情對她來說非常重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BVPGVrPjasR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBVPGVrPjasR&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=ee65808a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBVPGVrPjasR&h=0381bf7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BVPGVrPjasR</a><br />\n說到演藝圈的好交情，大家都不會忘記IU、劉寅娜這對好閨蜜！對IU來說友情是親情以外最大的支持，她還曾在頒獎典禮上公開告白：「雖然我們不是真正的親人，但妳是我最重要的人、我的頭號粉絲、我的超級巨星和我的繆斯女星，謝謝你劉寅娜！」<br />\n<br />\n9. 捐了8億幫助貧困兒童<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6emYojAfIB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6emYojAfIB&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=40282a5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6emYojAfIB&h=3675e81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6emYojAfIB</a><br />\n《富比士》（Forbes）雜誌曾列出「亞洲2019慈善英雄」，而IU就是排行榜中最年輕的一位，除了在疫情多次低調捐款，還捐給「綠色雨傘兒童財團」1億韓元，根據外媒報導，IU從2015年就不間斷的對兒童福利機構捐款，至今累積的款項甚至高達8億韓元（約台幣2,000萬）。<br />\n<br />\n10. 跟保鑣感情超好<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4bIs51HgCmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4bIs51HgCmk&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=c4bee91c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4bIs51HgCmk</a><br />\n有在追蹤IU的粉絲應該都知道她跟保鑣大叔的感情超要好～高挑壯碩的保鑣在IU旁邊就像是大樹一般，超萌對比可愛到不行！不管是撐傘、遞水，就連IU在演唱會走錯方向保鑣大叔也會把她拉回正途（笑）看著兩人有說有笑的模樣就相信IU的好人緣絕對是真的！"},{"pid":"44d020889649e4df14d18f774690410381894789","tid":2147838,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3561d638070859ad759d2966a2e1c89bb8b6046","tid":2147838,"uid":49004,"like":11,"dislike":11,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"跟銀赫感情超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd23d61abfab5aefca2717cce23b5f0b4503b8a","tid":2147838,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"人靚心善🥰"},{"pid":"30e6da54a4792a949347ead61ab625c6bb1ad64a","tid":2147838,"uid":36236,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"反U仲有咩說話好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咩有村假純正過佢嗰d全部on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8722cc611bd9c808cdffa19a2c9b31c301ba5718","tid":2147838,"uid":158372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"想做iu保鑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8148c28563fba57911013b7ddf5a73baf3bb9a5c","tid":2147838,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"今晚就J你啦"},{"pid":"0de756ec5ff4569aef738a8909d2138a8c72e415","tid":2147838,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"我❤️IU"},{"pid":"ac12f2baaf26063818be3915d2cd3ddf0e0ca7ea","tid":2147838,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"知恩好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f44dee790b7509a52b485f8d5be05a95f9173","tid":2147838,"uid":139242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"世上最完美女人"},{"pid":"24b9ab00a66eb3b47c6d3e332027ec972a9bd204","tid":2147838,"uid":154478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"世一iu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b319e26a559a8a61d041958d7eec15a2d4b1ed1","tid":2147838,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc87190e9f867b9c2754f15d5130ba9721c4b0d8","tid":2147838,"uid":33859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e6da54a4792a949347ead61ab625c6bb1ad64a","tid":2147838,"uid":36236,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"反U仲有咩說話好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咩有村假純正過佢嗰d全部on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"咁淫 唔反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}